17	//
18	// The basic approach is based on this article:
19	// http://www.drdobbs.com/parallel/rasterization-on-larrabee/217200602
20	// And is also described in "Hierarchical polygon tiling with coverage
21	// masks" Proceedings of ACM SIGGRAPH 93, Ned Greene.
